0:02:25.060,0:02:26.618
The past few days have been hot.

0:02:26.980,0:02:28.517
I heard from your nursemaid

0:02:28.517,0:02:30.689
that you have stayed up late studying every night.

0:02:30.871,0:02:32.697
Diligence is one thing -

0:02:32.697,0:02:34.730
but you must also take care of your health.

0:02:34.730,0:02:36.631
Mother, you had refreshments sent to me every night.

0:02:36.631,0:02:37.688
I don't feel tired.

0:02:38.351,0:02:41.751
The refreshments are meant as a reminder
 that it is time to rest,

0:02:42.051,0:02:43.935
rather than continuing your hard work.

0:02:44.200,0:02:45.491
I misunderstood.

0:02:45.718,0:02:47.480
Peace to Noble Consort Lumière, and the Fourth Prince.

0:02:47.480,0:02:49.264
- The night is cold and windy...
- Your Highness.

0:02:49.490,0:02:51.080
Why are you standing here alone?

0:02:51.080,0:02:52.593
His Majesty ordered me to come,

0:02:52.920,0:02:54.800
but the Third Prince is inside right now.

0:02:55.250,0:02:59.720
Mr. Su informed me that His Majesty is angered
and told me to wait outside for now.

0:03:01.550,0:03:05.263
I told you to recite Wei Zheng's 
“Ten Recommendations to Emperor Taizong”.

0:03:06.600,0:03:08.450
You recited it with no hesitation.

0:03:09.180,0:03:10.686
But when I asked you

0:03:10.890,0:03:15.400
how Taizong managed to "rule with a light hand,"

0:03:16.780,0:03:19.041
you faltered and couldn't give a clear answer.

0:03:20.070,0:03:25.320
Haven't you already learned from your shifu
about the "benevolent rule" of Taizong?

0:03:25.870,0:03:29.639
I've...  I've learned the "Zhenguan Zhengyao"...

0:03:30.040,0:03:33.200
Im... Imperial Mother told me to read it thoroughly.

0:03:33.750,0:03:36.253
Your shifu and Imperial Mother are very diligent.

0:03:36.480,0:03:38.254
But you are flippant and feckless!

0:03:39.670,0:03:41.174
You began your studies at the age of five.

0:03:41.800,0:03:43.594
More than a decade has since passed.

0:03:44.760,0:03:47.205
I don't know where all those years of studies have gone.

0:03:48.350,0:03:53.200
I remember two years ago, you could recite most of "Zhenguan Zhengyao."

0:03:54.230,0:03:57.153
But now you've forgotten everything!

0:03:58.760,0:04:00.486
It's fortunate that your shifu has a good temper.

0:04:01.080,0:04:02.240
If I were to teach you,

0:04:02.800,0:04:05.640
watching you study for a day would have killed me.

0:04:06.160,0:04:07.740
Imperial Father, please calm your anger.

0:04:07.740,0:04:10.466
Calm my anger? I wish I could!

0:04:11.460,0:04:15.429
But you don't allow me half a second of peace.

0:04:16.710,0:04:18.134
You are my eldest son.

0:04:19.000,0:04:22.800
I don't expect you to achieve greatness or to share my burden.

0:04:23.930,0:04:29.240
I only hope that you can be a good role model for your younger brothers,

0:04:29.760,0:04:31.480
so I have less to worry about.

0:04:32.560,0:04:36.200
But you persist in behaving like you're good for nothing!

0:04:37.000,0:04:38.529
His Majesty is so enraged.

0:04:39.849,0:04:41.520
His Majesty is the Son of Heaven.

0:04:42.640,0:04:45.719
He cannot be as mild-tempered or carefree as His Lordship.

0:04:46.320,0:04:47.836
His Lordship doesn't have children yet.

0:04:48.580,0:04:50.179
But if he does someday,

0:04:50.179,0:04:53.621
he might be even stricter than His Majesty
out of earnest paternal love.

0:04:54.400,0:04:55.840
By the way, Fourth Prince,

0:04:55.840,0:04:57.440
I heard that you have been studying rigorously.

0:04:57.710,0:04:59.768
Are you able to recite the books His Majesty mentioned?

0:05:00.200,0:05:02.090
I can't compare to my third brother.

0:05:02.090,0:05:03.560
I started my studies later than he did.

0:05:03.560,0:05:05.185
Your Highness said I study hard -

0:05:05.185,0:05:06.591
that's because I'm dull-witted.

0:05:06.591,0:05:08.220
I must spend more time studying

0:05:08.220,0:05:10.663
or else I will be scolded by my shifu.

0:05:10.800,0:05:13.524
Read and comprehend the essay within the next three days!

0:05:13.524,0:05:16.480
Don't come see me again
if you cannot grasp its content!

0:05:24.240,0:05:26.240
Greetings to Consort Lumière, and to Concubine Paix.

0:05:27.680,0:05:28.956
You should go inside now.

0:05:38.200,0:05:41.929
His Majesty was in an ireful mood.
His words were harsher than usual.

0:05:42.080,0:05:43.497
Don't take them to heart.

0:05:44.000,0:05:45.599
You are his son after all.

0:05:46.109,0:05:47.709
All will be well in a few days.

0:05:48.000,0:05:50.571
Yes, I thank Your Highness for your caring words.

0:05:52.010,0:05:54.397
You still need to return to your estate.

0:05:54.397,0:05:55.266
Go ahead.

0:05:55.480,0:05:58.480
Imperial Mother is waiting to go over my studies at her palace.

0:05:59.080,0:06:00.669
It's already so late.

0:06:01.800,0:06:05.166
At what time will you rise for class tomorrow?

0:06:05.480,0:06:06.560
At a quarter to four.

0:06:08.640,0:06:10.580
Do you sleep so few hours every day?

0:06:12.200,0:06:14.900
Imperial Mother says: "A clumsy bird needs to fly early."

0:06:15.240,0:06:18.780
I'm not as clever as others,
so I must be more diligent than them.

0:06:19.200,0:06:21.297
That's why I must study hard day and night.

0:06:21.590,0:06:23.299
The Empress wants you to nurture your ambitions.

0:06:23.670,0:06:25.309
But you also ought to take care of yourself.

0:06:26.260,0:06:29.440
I heard your Imperial Father has
started selecting a wife for you.

0:06:30.390,0:06:32.240
It's good to start your family early

0:06:32.240,0:06:34.260
so you will have someone to look after you.

0:06:34.260,0:06:35.141
Yes.

0:06:35.612,0:06:38.923
It's quite late, please allow me to take my leave.

0:06:44.270,0:06:46.730
Mother, you see how hardworking my third brother is.

0:06:48.110,0:06:49.400
I must work harder than him

0:06:49.950,0:06:51.713
so that Imperial Father will be fond of me.

0:06:52.700,0:06:54.310
You just told Concubine Paix

0:06:55.370,0:06:57.663
that you haven't memorized all the essays His Majesty mentioned.

0:06:58.250,0:07:00.462
But a few days back, I heard you recite them fluently

0:07:00.750,0:07:02.924
and your comprehension was profound.

0:07:03.420,0:07:05.130
Mother, I've observed how you keep a low profile.

0:07:05.130,0:07:07.547
"My eyes and ears have been immersed,"
so I understand what I should do.

0:07:08.260,0:07:09.412
You are smart.

0:07:09.590,0:07:12.800
Mother and son "share the same pulse."
Of course I'm like you.

0:07:16.390,0:07:19.310
Mother, my third brother is the eldest son.

0:07:19.310,0:07:20.597
Will he become the Emperor?

0:07:21.810,0:07:22.977
I don't know.

0:07:23.190,0:07:25.020
But my sixth brother was born to you

0:07:25.020,0:07:26.591
and Imperial Father adores him the most.

0:07:26.591,0:07:27.720
So he will be crowned.

0:07:27.780,0:07:29.240
As long as my sixth brother becomes the Emperor,

0:07:29.240,0:07:30.400
I will be happy.

0:07:32.610,0:07:33.809
Your sixth brother is still young,

0:07:35.030,0:07:38.320
and I don't wish for him to be the emperor.

0:07:40.160,0:07:41.920
Only the most worthy of all

0:07:42.460,0:07:44.626
is capable of ruling the Empire.

0:07:45.380,0:07:46.398
Do you understand?

0:07:47.250,0:07:47.919
Yes.

0:07:50.590,0:07:53.210
Hongshi, do any of these ladies catch your eye?

0:07:55.050,0:07:58.693
Mother, you're benevolent to ask. 
Allow me to obey your decision.

0:07:59.020,0:08:00.584
Choose whomever you prefer

0:08:00.584,0:08:03.390
and inform your Imperial Father yourself.

0:08:04.060,0:08:05.520
You've grown up.

0:08:05.520,0:08:07.270
I will only make arrangements

0:08:07.270,0:08:08.999
and not decisions for you.

0:08:15.200,0:08:15.940
Greetings, Your Highness.

0:08:16.830,0:08:18.780
Peace to Noble Consort Lumière.

0:08:20.790,0:08:22.406
Peace and grace to Your Majesty.

0:08:22.620,0:08:23.580
Rise.

0:08:23.830,0:08:24.669
I thank Your Majesty.

0:08:28.250,0:08:29.033
You all may rise.

0:08:29.710,0:08:31.580
I thank Your Noble Highness.

0:08:32.380,0:08:33.930
This is the first time we meet

0:08:33.930,0:08:35.420
and perhaps the first of many.

0:08:37.220,0:08:39.040
The Third Prince has grown taller.

0:08:39.140,0:08:40.770
The weather is pleasantly cooler today.

0:08:40.770,0:08:42.633
I invited you and Noble Consort Estime

0:08:42.633,0:08:45.301
to aid in choosing exceptional young ladies.

0:08:52.990,0:08:55.154
Every one of them looks perfect to me!

0:08:55.990,0:08:57.450
Take your time -

0:08:57.450,0:08:58.739
you'll find the outstanding one.

0:09:02.660,0:09:04.234
Her Majesty invited us here

0:09:05.250,0:09:07.790
so we can chime in with our support

0:09:08.420,0:09:10.000
if the Third Prince has a preference.

0:09:11.550,0:09:14.340
She doesn't want others to think
she made the decision on her own;

0:09:14.340,0:09:15.884
it will look like we all approve.

0:09:17.140,0:09:18.362
Who is in the Empress's favor?

0:09:18.640,0:09:19.720
Her own niece.

0:09:20.060,0:09:22.560
The one dressed in green. Her name is Qingying.

0:09:23.560,0:09:25.920
Qingying, come over and greet the Third Prince.

0:09:26.390,0:09:26.970
Yes.

0:09:31.520,0:09:32.800
Greetings, Third Prince.

0:09:33.690,0:09:37.193
This is my cousin's youngest daughter.
You can call her your cousin.

0:09:38.780,0:09:39.831
Cousin.

0:09:40.030,0:09:41.807
Third Prince, my maiden name is Qingying.

0:09:47.762,0:09:51.682
These flowers are just as pretty as the peonies
in Imperial Mother's palace.

0:09:53.050,0:09:54.581
Thank you for the kind words, Princess.

0:09:56.220,0:09:57.920
Longyue, come here.

0:10:00.350,0:10:03.050
Longyue, the myrtle trees over there are blooming.

0:10:03.470,0:10:05.612
- How about we go check them out?
- Hmm, yes.

0:10:06.520,0:10:08.438
The myrtle flowers are the finest in my palace.

0:10:08.650,0:10:10.730
You may all view them as you please.

0:10:11.980,0:10:13.600
We take our leave, Your Majesty.

0:10:26.660,0:10:28.750
Prince, I heard you like gingered plums,

0:10:29.330,0:10:30.490
may I offer you some?

0:10:32.340,0:10:33.579
Oh these plums?

0:10:34.006,0:10:36.760
It's not that I particularly like them.

0:10:36.760,0:10:38.240
Imperial Mother says that

0:10:38.260,0:10:40.720
plums stimulate the appetite, and ginger warms the Stomach,

0:10:41.300,0:10:43.460
so she encourages me to have them.

0:10:44.180,0:10:46.590
Her Majesty truly cares about your well-being, Prince.

0:10:46.980,0:10:48.913
You ought to follow Her Majesty's advice.

0:10:52.110,0:10:54.253
You don't seem to like children, do you?

0:10:54.690,0:10:56.160
Children are naughty and careless.

0:10:57.273,0:10:59.680
Grown-ups shouldn't mind their mistakes.

0:11:00.000,0:11:02.124
We don't need to pay attention to them.

0:11:02.620,0:11:05.640
I had this dress made especially for meeting you, Prince.

0:11:06.490,0:11:08.330
How could I let someone damage it?

0:11:11.500,0:11:13.312
I see. Longyue, come here.

0:11:16.090,0:11:18.040
Here’s your favorite, gingered plums.

0:11:18.210,0:11:19.260
They’re all yours.

0:11:19.260,0:11:20.970
Third Brother, you are the best to me!

0:11:20.970,0:11:21.667
Enjoy!

0:11:24.800,0:11:27.383
Longyue, let’s go. I’ll take you to see the flowers.

0:11:32.480,0:11:35.440
Perhaps the young people are feeling 
a bit inhibited because of our presence.

0:11:36.860,0:11:38.150
It's getting windy.

0:11:38.150,0:11:41.174
Noble Consort Lumière, I’ll return and get changed.

0:11:45.580,0:11:46.780
I can’t find Mother!

0:11:46.780,0:11:48.821
Will Your Highness help me look for her?

0:11:51.080,0:11:52.196
Go ahead.

0:11:52.420,0:11:53.870
I bid Your Majesty goodbye.

0:12:02.680,0:12:03.783
I'm here!

0:12:04.550,0:12:06.049
How did you leave the garden without notice.

0:12:06.720,0:12:08.323
Fortunately, the Empress didn't fault you for that.

0:12:08.720,0:12:10.230
She isn't thinking of that now;

0:12:10.230,0:12:13.534
she’s too engrossed in the glory and wealth
of her Ula-Nara clan.

0:12:13.845,0:12:15.760
She doesn't care what we do.

0:12:15.770,0:12:18.020
You looked so bored sitting there.

0:12:18.020,0:12:20.404
So I came up with an excuse for Longyue to get you out.

0:12:21.530,0:12:23.640
Just look at those young ladies. 
Each one is remarkable.

0:12:24.110,0:12:25.904
But the Third Prince seems indifferent.

0:12:26.990,0:12:28.030
That's true.

0:12:28.030,0:12:31.664
Longyue, your third brother looks dispirited.

0:12:31.870,0:12:33.210
Go ask him to join us.

0:12:33.210,0:12:35.750
Invite him to take a walk and relax.

0:12:35.750,0:12:36.501
Hurry.

0:12:50.560,0:12:54.577
Third brother, why don't you like those pretty girls?

0:12:55.140,0:12:57.180
I don’t like conceited women.

0:12:57.491,0:12:59.512
Or pretentious women.

0:12:59.900,0:13:02.270
Me too. I don’t like such women, either.

0:13:02.270,0:13:04.425
Then, what kind of women do you like?

0:13:05.410,0:13:06.900
Gentle... and serene.

0:13:08.070,0:13:09.940
You think I’m too much of a chatterbox?

0:13:10.410,0:13:12.198
Not at all. You’re most adorable!

0:13:14.290,0:13:18.480
Why has this flower changed color?
Mother brought me here this morning.

0:13:19.340,0:13:21.056
This flower is called “a beauty's visage”.

0:13:21.550,0:13:23.750
It is red at sunrise and turns pink when the sun sets.

0:13:24.420,0:13:27.510
The color is as fleeting as the expressions on a beauty's face.

0:13:27.510,0:13:30.277
Laughing or frowning as her mood changes.

0:13:30.640,0:13:35.043
This sister in front of us has the “visage of a beauty”.
Third brother, don't you think so?

0:13:35.940,0:13:41.206
"The renowned peony mudan, paired with
her beauty which could topple a nation."

0:13:46.610,0:13:48.600
Princess, I don't deserve being called "sister."

0:13:48.950,0:13:50.463
I am Noble Lady Lustré.

0:13:51.120,0:13:53.909
Noble Lady Lustré? How is it I’ve never met you?

0:13:54.370,0:13:55.460
And you are…?

0:13:55.460,0:13:56.788
This is my third brother.

0:13:59.000,0:14:00.291
Peace to the Third Prince.

0:14:01.290,0:14:04.960
Third brother, Noble Lady Lustré counts as one of our mothers.

0:14:05.210,0:14:08.350
You hardly visit the harem.
That's why you don’t know her.

0:14:11.220,0:14:12.640
Peace to Your Highness.

0:14:12.720,0:14:15.180
Peace to third brother, peace to Your Highness.

0:14:15.640,0:14:17.035
Peace to everyone!

0:14:17.560,0:14:21.374
Your Highness seems pensive, contemplating the flowers alone.

0:14:22.650,0:14:24.534
I was just thinking of my family at home.

0:14:25.400,0:14:26.987
They can’t come visit you in the palace?

0:14:27.490,0:14:30.240
It's a short reunion, and then more time apart.

0:14:32.700,0:14:34.237
My birth mother passed away.

0:14:34.910,0:14:36.364
I can't see her even if I wanted to.

0:14:37.250,0:14:38.790
Prince, please don’t have a heavy heart.

0:14:38.790,0:14:40.983
Although your birth mother is no longer here,

0:14:41.170,0:14:43.920
she is still watching over you wherever you are.

0:14:45.170,0:14:47.170
And all her actions in her life

0:14:47.170,0:14:48.957
would have been done for your benefit.

0:14:50.220,0:14:51.958
I thank Your Highness for such a thoughtful perspective.

0:14:53.720,0:14:56.310
Why is Your Highness unattended by a servant?

0:14:56.310,0:14:58.114
What difference would a servant make?

0:14:58.310,0:15:01.943
Having a companion who doesn’t understand you
is no better than being alone.

0:15:03.900,0:15:06.510
It's true. Sometimes it seems there would be comfort in a crowd

0:15:07.690,0:15:09.060
but often,

0:15:09.900,0:15:13.110
the bigger the crowd, the lonlier one can feel.

0:15:16.370,0:15:18.354
You're right about that, Prince.

0:15:19.080,0:15:21.669
It’s getting late. Allow me to take my leave.

0:15:32.510,0:15:34.599
One can be lonely however many companions there are.

0:15:35.760,0:15:39.560
Only a true confidante's companionship
 can bring happiness.

0:15:40.310,0:15:43.061
What are you mumbling, third brother?

0:15:45.480,0:15:47.190
It's nothing. Let’s go.

0:16:13.430,0:16:16.340
Imperial Noble Consort is the best pipa player in the entire palace.

0:16:17.560,0:16:19.554
Noble Consort Lumière is the best on the qin zither.

0:16:20.350,0:16:23.040
But on the zheng zither, you are the best.

0:16:24.770,0:16:28.380
My slight skills can't compare with Their Highnesses'.

0:16:28.980,0:16:31.770
You have a calm nature and never vie for favor.

0:16:32.110,0:16:33.952
You certainly have your good qualities.

0:16:40.290,0:16:42.780
Your Majesty, the Third Prince is here.

0:16:43.370,0:16:44.330
Show him in.

0:16:44.330,0:16:45.039
Yes.

0:16:47.750,0:16:49.240
Your Majesty, I shall take my leave.

0:16:49.300,0:16:52.130
No need to leave. You're his elder.

0:17:04.980,0:17:05.968
Peace to Imperial Father.

0:17:08.110,0:17:09.600
What brings you here at this hour?

0:17:09.820,0:17:11.151
Have you finished reviewing your schoolwork?

0:17:11.440,0:17:12.200
Yes. I’ve reviewed all of it.

0:17:12.570,0:17:15.070
I also studied the essays that were covered in class.

0:17:15.070,0:17:16.014
That’s good.

0:17:16.740,0:17:18.990
I’ll quiz you on it another day.

0:17:18.990,0:17:20.000
Imperial Father,

0:17:20.000,0:17:21.920
actually, I'm here about my schooling.

0:17:21.920,0:17:23.490
I would like to ask for your permission.

0:17:23.660,0:17:24.370
Go ahead.

0:17:25.080,0:17:27.508
Imperial Father and Mother think I've grown up

0:17:27.508,0:17:29.166
and that it's time I establish a family.

0:17:29.290,0:17:32.206
But I think I should prioritize my studies right now,

0:17:33.340,0:17:35.371
instead of indulging myself in affairs of the heart.

0:17:35.590,0:17:38.559
So I'd rather not get married yet.

0:17:38.800,0:17:42.520
Your mother and I had the intention
to find someone to look after you.

0:17:43.100,0:17:45.440
I’m already well looked after by my servants.

0:17:46.230,0:17:48.854
Having a wife will inevitably distract me from my studies.

0:17:49.230,0:17:53.000
I know that I am too incompetent to share
any of your burdens, Imperial Father.

0:17:53.110,0:17:56.506
So I aspire to stay dedicated and not worry you.

0:17:57.700,0:17:59.860
I am relieved you think this way.

0:18:00.240,0:18:02.560
This was your Imperial Mother’s idea in the first place.

0:18:02.580,0:18:04.000
I’m in no hurry for you to wed.

0:18:04.080,0:18:07.360
Imperial Father, I hope I'll marry

0:18:07.767,0:18:09.617
a virtuous and gentle wife one day.

0:18:10.170,0:18:13.128
Indeed. Marital harmony matters the most.

0:18:14.760,0:18:15.880
You may leave now.

0:18:15.880,0:18:16.754
Yes.

0:18:20.510,0:18:22.165
Noble Lady Lustré plays the zheng as if

0:18:22.388,0:18:25.858
"chiming the Kunlun Mountains jade,"
or "the drip of dew onto lotus flowers."

0:18:26.930,0:18:28.399
I admire Your Higness's talent.

0:18:29.600,0:18:31.034
Thank you for the compliment, Third Prince.

0:18:31.610,0:18:32.800
You have a good ear.

0:18:33.320,0:18:36.310
"High Mountain and Flowing Water"
is Noble Lady Lustré's best piece.

0:18:38.490,0:18:39.200
Go on.

0:18:39.570,0:18:40.310
Yes.

0:18:47.660,0:18:49.120
Madam Autumn, please stay.

0:18:49.120,0:18:50.311
Please wait, My Lady.

0:18:50.750,0:18:51.942
What is it, Madam?

0:18:52.340,0:18:54.352
Although you can't become the primary wife right now,

0:18:54.670,0:18:56.486
Her Majesty had a valid point.

0:18:57.210,0:18:59.260
Why don't you set aside concern for the title,

0:18:59.260,0:19:01.630
and for now, serve the Third Prince as his concubine?

0:19:02.050,0:19:03.674
You can then be promoted later.

0:19:03.850,0:19:06.509
My aunt's lowest title was still Lord Consort.

0:19:07.180,0:19:09.766
Now she wants me to be just a titleless concubine?

0:19:10.480,0:19:12.278
I can see how much she cares for me!

0:19:12.520,0:19:14.143
You should think long-term, My Lady.

0:19:14.690,0:19:16.323
"Endure the indignity and carry the heaviness."

0:19:16.860,0:19:17.931
Endure the indignity?

0:19:18.690,0:19:20.752
Haven't I endured enough humiliation already?

0:19:21.320,0:19:23.024
The Third Prince doesn't cast his eyes on me.

0:19:23.240,0:19:25.513
Even His Majesty agrees the Third Prince won't be selecting a wife.

0:19:25.950,0:19:28.081
I'm already the laughingstock of the palace.

0:19:28.660,0:19:31.642
Should I shamelessly shove my face in his? 
Then how would I be seen?

0:19:32.120,0:19:34.863
Please tell my aunt how thankful I am
for her generous condiseration.

0:19:36.340,0:19:37.286
Take care, My Lady.

0:19:46.850,0:19:47.716
Your Majesty.

0:19:48.020,0:19:48.979
Has she been sent off?

0:19:49.980,0:19:52.310
Yes. Lady Qingying wasn't happy.

0:19:53.060,0:19:54.850
Did you convey my message?

0:19:55.440,0:19:57.480
Yes, but My Lady Qingying was too high-minded to comply.

0:20:01.320,0:20:03.647
She's still young, and impetuous.

0:20:04.620,0:20:07.110
It wouldn't matter now if she is the wife or a concubine.

0:20:08.080,0:20:10.327
Once the Third Prince succeeds to the throne,

0:20:10.620,0:20:12.666
I will become the Empress Dowager.

0:20:12.920,0:20:16.660
It will be up to me to decide who is the next Empress.

0:20:17.670,0:20:21.040
The Empress must come from the Ula-Nara family.

0:20:21.550,0:20:22.851
Your Majesty is correct.

0:20:23.050,0:20:25.677
Lady Qingying is still too young to understand this.

0:20:26.220,0:20:28.624
What a shame she wouldn't comply.

0:20:29.180,0:20:32.469
The Ula-Nara family does not lack suitable girls.

0:20:33.270,0:20:37.140
Once the younger ones grow old enough,
there will be no place for her here.

0:20:37.520,0:20:39.534
It's because she doesn't appreciate Your Majesty's favor.

0:20:39.860,0:20:43.400
She even dared to remark on the fact that
Your Majesty was once a lord consort.

0:20:43.700,0:20:44.780
Very well.

0:20:45.610,0:20:48.570
Since she likes to speak of my lord consortship,

0:20:49.240,0:20:51.200
and also despises becoming a concubine,

0:20:51.200,0:20:53.687
then I will help her out once more.

0:20:54.420,0:21:00.702
She will learn that being the lord consort of another prince
cannot compare to being a concubine of the Third Prince.

0:21:01.380,0:21:02.620
Your Majesty means...

0:21:03.300,0:21:05.174
The Fourth Prince has turned sixteen.

0:21:05.470,0:21:07.296
I will go and ask His Majesty

0:21:08.100,0:21:11.880
to betroth Qingying to the Fourth Prince as his lord consort.

0:21:12.680,0:21:14.400
Isn't that too flattering for the Fourth Prince?

0:21:14.600,0:21:15.389
Flattering?

0:21:16.560,0:21:19.218
The Fourth Prince gets the Third Prince's cast-off.

0:21:19.407,0:21:21.690
And Noble Consort Lumière is not on good terms with me.

0:21:21.690,0:21:23.948
Gaining such a daughter-in-law

0:21:23.948,0:21:25.664
will cause only trouble for her.

0:21:26.610,0:21:27.990
Your Highness has a discerning mind.

0:21:27.990,0:21:29.600
But there is one thing I don't understand.

0:21:29.950,0:21:31.990
The imperial court has already raised
 the need to establish a crown prince.

0:21:32.450,0:21:34.754
Why did Your Majesty encourage them
to suggest the Sixth Prince?

0:21:35.290,0:21:36.622
His Majesty is distrustful.

0:21:36.790,0:21:41.894
Any collusion between the court and the harem
 is strictly prohibited.

0:21:42.710,0:21:46.170
We must often remind His Majesty of who is colluding.

