0:21:53.913,0:21:57.655
These past few years, I feel my health is nowhere near what it was.

0:21:58.902,0:22:02.321
The Empress wanted to find a wife for Hongshi,

0:22:03.860,0:22:07.350
and again, the imperial court brought up choosing a crown prince.

0:22:08.860,0:22:10.669
You have no idea how fed up I am.

0:22:11.950,0:22:14.410
Do all these officials think that I'm already so old

0:22:14.910,0:22:17.450
that I must choose a crown prince now?

0:22:17.960,0:22:19.427
Si Lang, you are in your prime years.

0:22:19.427,0:22:21.170
There's no rush to name a crown prince.

0:22:21.170,0:22:22.950
The Third Prince is promising but he needs more experience.

0:22:23.840,0:22:26.883
The court officials are simply concerned about how hard you work.

0:22:27.034,0:22:29.378
They just wish someone could share the weight you carry.

0:22:31.260,0:22:33.013
Even if I am to choose a crown prince,

0:22:34.220,0:22:36.603
I want to wait for the Sixth Prince to grow up.

0:22:38.850,0:22:42.970
Instead of worrying about what they should, 
they worry over things they shouldn't.

0:22:44.020,0:22:46.720
Speaking of which, the Fourth Prince has turned sixteen.

0:22:47.280,0:22:51.493
Speaking of the Third Prince's marriage
also has me thinking of the Fourth Prince's.

0:22:51.780,0:22:53.991
Don't play favorites, Your Majesty.

0:22:54.330,0:22:56.660
You and the Empress are of the same mind.

0:22:57.660,0:23:02.960
The Empress has brought up her niece Qingying.
She wants to betroth her to Hongli.

0:23:03.380,0:23:04.731
Her Majesty is not being fair -

0:23:05.050,0:23:07.880
shoving her to the Fourth Prince
because the Third Prince doesn't like her.

0:23:08.470,0:23:13.259
Your Majesty said you had your eye on a girl surnamed Fuca,
daughter of Chahar's General Li.

0:23:13.760,0:23:15.320
An emperor cannot take back his words.

0:23:16.520,0:23:18.721
I know you also like Fuca.

0:23:18.980,0:23:20.890
Although she is a year younger than Hongli,

0:23:20.890,0:23:22.293
she has a stable personality.

0:23:22.860,0:23:25.731
But the Empress said Qingying only wants the title of Lord Consort.

0:23:26.820,0:23:29.930
Her request is a modest one so I didn't refuse it.

0:23:30.240,0:23:32.490
The Ula-Nara clan is a prominent lineage.

0:23:32.490,0:23:36.007
I'm afraid Her Majesty's niece will feel aggrieved at this title.

0:23:36.240,0:23:41.240
The Empress was disposed towards it.
I will not make her lose face.

0:23:41.920,0:23:45.660
Just as well. The Fourth Prince benefits from this after all.

0:23:48.420,0:23:50.790
The weather is lovely today. Let's go for a stroll.

0:23:51.220,0:23:54.590
If we stay inside every day, we'll grow moldy before long!

0:23:55.680,0:23:57.104
It's already September.

0:23:57.310,0:24:00.000
Did you have your servants collect willow branches for you?

0:24:00.230,0:24:01.010
What for?

0:24:02.020,0:24:05.360
"Willow" sounds like "stay", and the "ninth" month sounds like "long."

0:24:05.360,0:24:07.915
It is a wish for His Majesty to "stay long" in your palace.

0:24:08.570,0:24:10.164
I don't believe in that kind of thing.

0:24:10.164,0:24:13.190
You're currently in favor, 
that's why you don't believe in it!

0:24:18.040,0:24:19.520
Isn't that His Lordship?

0:24:21.040,0:24:22.080
Noble Prince Guo.

0:24:30.675,0:24:32.720
It's been so long since I last saw Your Lordship.

0:24:32.720,0:24:37.540
Since Your Lordship got married,
you can't be as carefree as in the past.

0:24:38.010,0:24:42.052
With one lord consort on the left and another on the right,

0:24:42.052,0:24:45.440
Your Lordship cannot escape even with wings!

0:24:46.610,0:24:48.545
Your Noble Highness is always so humorous.

0:24:49.360,0:24:50.546
It's been a long time.

0:24:52.820,0:24:54.379
Noble Consort Lumière, have you been well?

0:24:56.950,0:25:00.000
I thank Your Lordship for asking. 
I'm in good health.

0:25:04.160,0:25:06.200
What brings Your Lordship to the palace today?

0:25:06.920,0:25:09.440
I'm here to pay my respects to His Majesty.

0:25:13.420,0:25:16.174
It's windy. Please put on your cloak, Your Lordship.

0:25:19.890,0:25:20.960
Thank you.

0:25:24.730,0:25:27.599
We're husband and wife -
 "thank-you's" are for strangers.

0:25:29.360,0:25:31.040
This must be Lord Consort Xian.

0:25:31.900,0:25:34.606
I am Meng Jingxian, lord consort of Noble Prince Guo.

0:25:34.990,0:25:36.499
Peace to Your Noble Highness.

0:25:36.944,0:25:40.280
I wish Your Highness eternal happiness and unending grace.

0:25:40.280,0:25:41.161
Please rise.

0:25:42.870,0:25:44.660
You were ill on your wedding day

0:25:45.290,0:25:46.802
and this is my first time meeting you.

0:25:47.330,0:25:50.120
We're a family, there's no need to be so formal.

0:25:50.590,0:25:52.640
I should have paid my respects to Your Noble Highness earlier,

0:25:53.010,0:25:54.504
but my health hasn't allowed me.

0:25:55.340,0:25:57.767
In fact, I came to the palace for two reasons today:

0:25:58.300,0:26:00.320
To pay my respects to His Majesty

0:26:00.320,0:26:02.614
and to ask forgiveness of Your Highnesses.

0:26:03.470,0:26:06.184
Both His Majesty and I have been
thinking about Your Ladyship's health.

0:26:07.230,0:26:10.199
Why didn't Yuyin come along
to pay her respects to His Majesty today?

0:26:10.690,0:26:12.282
How she's forgotten the rules!

0:26:12.440,0:26:15.180
Since Your Ladyship serves His Lordship alongside Yuyin,

0:26:15.690,0:26:18.481
please educate her on my behalf
when you have a chance.

0:26:19.160,0:26:21.120
Today, the farming estates are reporting their harvest.

0:26:21.120,0:26:24.060
Yuyin is attending to it, so she was unable to come.

0:26:25.080,0:26:27.430
Yuyin is so skillful with domestic matters.

0:26:28.080,0:26:30.581
Unlike me, with my ill health,

0:26:31.500,0:26:33.176
I'm only a burden to others.

0:26:36.010,0:26:37.460
Your Ladyship's worrying too much.

0:26:37.880,0:26:40.000
I heard you're versed in poetry and literature.

0:26:40.340,0:26:41.843
How can you be a burden?

0:26:44.100,0:26:46.340
Jingxian, don't overthink.

0:26:49.350,0:26:51.560
Yuyin is Your Noble Highness's honorary sister.

0:26:52.150,0:26:54.390
If Your Noble Highness doesn't mind my dullness,

0:26:55.280,0:26:57.560
please see me like a younger sister as well.

0:26:58.860,0:27:00.960
Your Lordship overly flatters me.

0:27:04.490,0:27:06.888
It's getting late. We shouldn't leave His Majesty waiting.

0:27:10.290,0:27:14.622
Aiya! Your Lordship treats Lord Consort Xian so kindly.

0:27:14.622,0:27:17.623
No less than how you treat Noble Consort Lumière's sister.

0:27:17.880,0:27:22.466
It seems the left- and right-hand consorts
are "equally sharing the spring scenery."

0:27:22.466,0:27:24.466
Your Lordship is really a loving husband.

0:27:29.690,0:27:31.396
We shall take our leave.

0:27:39.839,0:27:42.648
Just after Your Highness arrived,
Her Noble Highness has returned.

0:27:47.910,0:27:50.000
It's rare to see you here, Paix.

0:27:51.170,0:27:53.869
Does Your Noble Highness always have so many servants around?

0:27:57.340,0:27:59.436
You may all leave if not on service.

0:28:00.550,0:28:02.220
A cold wind blew through the imperial garden today.

0:28:02.220,0:28:04.130
The chill could have entered Your Noble Highness's chest.

0:28:04.760,0:28:06.356
Quickly warm it with a sip of tea.

0:28:06.680,0:28:07.822
You saw them too?

0:28:08.020,0:28:10.310
I've long heard of Lord Consort Xian's devotion.

0:28:10.930,0:28:12.707
"Seeing is better than hearing a hundred times."

0:28:14.270,0:28:16.309
Where were you hiding to watch that show?

0:28:17.940,0:28:21.887
Life is tough. One always has to put on a show.

0:28:22.740,0:28:26.209
But within this palace especially,
there are good shows everywhere you go.

0:28:27.030,0:28:29.740
So you think Lord Consort Xian
was just putting on an act?

0:28:30.500,0:28:34.860
Some acts may appear fake, yet the feelings are true.

0:28:35.920,0:28:39.259
Your Highness feels uncomfortable
after seeing only one act of the show.

0:28:40.260,0:28:45.830
I wonder how Lord Consort Yu feels
seeing Xian's devotion day after day.

0:28:46.720,0:28:48.089
Yuyin is not like that.

0:28:49.390,0:28:51.472
Don't underestimate the jealousy in a woman's heart.

0:28:52.640,0:28:53.982
Ever since their wedding,

0:28:54.390,0:28:56.640
Lord Consort Yu has been the one to 
accompany His Lordship to the palace.

0:28:57.230,0:29:00.770
But now that Lord Consort Xian has improved her health,

0:29:01.820,0:29:07.440
I'm afraid Lord Consort Yu may finally  taste neglect
amidst managing all the estate affairs.

0:29:07.700,0:29:08.745
She won't.

0:29:09.122,0:29:12.610
At the moment, they are on equal footings.

0:29:13.040,0:29:16.051
Precisely because of their equal and balanced status,

0:29:16.630,0:29:18.754
if His Lordship shows more favor for one,

0:29:19.590,0:29:24.170
the neglected one could become narrow-minded and be unable to bear it.

0:29:26.090,0:29:28.509
Why His Lordship married Yuyin -

0:29:29.237,0:29:31.752
Your Noble Highness knows better than I do.

0:29:32.980,0:29:34.688
How could that little portrait

0:29:34.688,0:29:36.560
fall out easily for no reason?

0:29:38.190,0:29:40.664
His Lordship is not a careless man.

0:29:42.990,0:29:44.466
"The wood has been made into a boat."

0:29:45.030,0:29:46.720
Concubine Paix, you should understand

0:29:46.720,0:29:49.516
one can rely only on what they hold in their two hands.

0:29:50.120,0:29:51.334
But you and I

0:29:51.540,0:29:53.833
lost the chance to be in Yuyin's position a long time ago.

0:29:54.870,0:29:58.222
She acted in her own interest,
but that's understandable.

0:30:00.710,0:30:03.141
"Heaven destroys those who don't act in their own interest."

0:30:03.760,0:30:07.679
Lord Consort Yu must not lose sight of her conscience.

0:30:08.760,0:30:10.429
I'll go back and restore my energy.

0:30:11.050,0:30:13.681
I'm sure there are endless good shows to come.

0:30:14.140,0:30:15.429
I don't want to miss them.

0:30:18.150,0:30:19.266
I'll take my leave.

0:30:28.910,0:30:32.324
Does Your Noble Highness know why
all the imperial concubines love to eat sweets?

0:30:33.620,0:30:35.318
For the bitterness in their hearts,

0:30:35.318,0:30:37.326
sweets are probably the only remedy.

0:30:38.080,0:30:39.680
Then Your Highness should eat some more.

0:30:39.960,0:30:43.554
There is no need to take Concubine Paix's words to heart.

0:30:44.170,0:30:45.051
That's true.

0:30:47.260,0:30:50.334
Yuyin will visit the palace in a couple days.

0:30:51.090,0:30:53.267
Be sure to prepare her favorite snacks in advance.

0:30:53.720,0:30:54.300
Yes.

0:31:05.400,0:31:06.619
Noble Lady.

0:31:07.030,0:31:08.092
Third Prince.

0:31:09.910,0:31:11.190
You should address me the same way as other concubines.

0:31:11.780,0:31:13.120
It's just the two of us.

0:31:17.290,0:31:18.734
Peace to Your Highness.

0:31:20.040,0:31:22.295
- You may go now.
- Yes.

0:31:27.920,0:31:29.786
Third Prince, do you have something to tell me?

0:31:30.340,0:31:33.798
I added lyrics to your "High Mountain and Flowing Water".

0:31:33.798,0:31:35.268
Have you heard my version yet?

0:31:36.390,0:31:38.056
Third Prince, please don't talk about that!

0:31:38.310,0:31:40.390
If His Majesty knows you are not focused on your studies,

0:31:40.390,0:31:41.780
he will scold you again.

0:31:44.400,0:31:45.341
I knew it.

0:31:45.520,0:31:48.025
In this palace, you're the only one who cares about me.

0:31:48.025,0:31:49.740
Only you understand me.

0:31:49.740,0:31:51.236
Third Prince, what are you doing?

0:31:51.236,0:31:52.929
I am your father's concubine!

0:31:53.620,0:31:54.843
You are good to me!

0:31:54.843,0:31:57.213
- I don't care about the title or status!
- Stay back!

0:31:58.580,0:32:00.204
Am I nothing next to my Imperial Father?!

0:32:00.500,0:32:02.637
I have you in my heart!
He's already an old man!

0:32:13.140,0:32:14.470
What's going on today?

0:32:14.470,0:32:16.731
Noble Lady Lustré looks flustered

0:32:16.731,0:32:20.960
and the Third Prince seems as if he's lost his soul.

0:32:21.060,0:32:23.020
Their blood and qi are so firey.

0:32:23.020,0:32:24.210
I'm afraid they...

0:32:24.633,0:32:26.247
No wonder...

0:32:26.610,0:32:32.000
I heard the performers rehearsing a lyric version of
Noble Lady Lustré's "High Mountain and Flowing Water."

0:32:32.610,0:32:36.480
It seems that the Third Prince ordered it
based on Lady Lustré's melody.

0:32:36.990,0:32:38.290
Your Highness is saying...

0:32:38.290,0:32:40.864
The Third Prince is the foster son of the Empress.

0:32:41.460,0:32:43.169
The Empress is his mother.

0:32:44.420,0:32:46.234
This is a serious matter.

0:32:47.290,0:32:48.687
Have someone keep an eye out.

0:32:49.000,0:32:50.000
Yes.

0:32:52.050,0:32:54.103
You've already stayed here for a few days.

0:32:55.090,0:32:58.259
His Lordship will worry if you don't return soon.

0:32:58.930,0:33:01.290
His Lordship treats Meng Jingxian better than me

0:33:01.882,0:33:04.160
and the servants have become snobbish.

0:33:05.690,0:33:07.360
I see no point in going back.

0:33:08.940,0:33:12.000
Your Highness, Lord Consort Xian is here
from Noble Prince Guo's estate.

0:33:12.826,0:33:15.771
She said she wishes to pay respects to Your Highness.

0:33:16.530,0:33:17.940
"Speak of Cao Cao and he arrives".

0:33:18.490,0:33:20.490
It's true that we can't talk about others behind their back.

0:33:20.490,0:33:22.101
Elder sister, I don't want to see her.

0:33:22.450,0:33:25.420
I've already seen enough of her fawning over His Lordship.

0:33:25.420,0:33:27.495
That's why I'm here - to avoid her and have some quiet!

0:33:27.495,0:33:29.122
Why can't I just have some peace?

0:33:29.540,0:33:30.931
"What one doesn't see brings one peace."

0:33:31.300,0:33:33.575
Go hide over there. I'll handle her.

0:33:35.097,0:33:36.963
-Your Highness.
- Show her in.

0:33:49.900,0:33:51.826
Peace to Noble Consort Lumière.

0:33:53.150,0:33:54.123
Rise.

0:33:55.406,0:33:56.457
Have a seat.

0:33:57.700,0:34:01.139
What brings you here to visit today?

0:34:02.580,0:34:04.466
I came to pay my respects to His Majesty

0:34:04.700,0:34:06.266
and decided to visit Your Highness as well.

0:34:06.870,0:34:10.846
I heard Yuyin has been staying here for the last few days.

0:34:11.710,0:34:13.740
But I don't see her around.

0:34:14.550,0:34:17.894
You just missed her; she just left to visit Noble Consort Estime.

0:34:18.130,0:34:20.829
She wants to sew some clothes for Princess Longyue.

0:34:22.140,0:34:24.406
Yuyin is so fond of children.

0:34:25.560,0:34:26.879
Have some tea.

0:34:35.190,0:34:37.026
Your Highness's tea is so fragrant.

0:34:37.650,0:34:40.000
But my condition makes tea unsuitable for me.

0:34:40.200,0:34:42.860
Otherwise, I would love to savor this fine tea.

0:34:43.370,0:34:45.781
What's wrong? Is Your Ladyship unwell?

0:34:46.330,0:34:47.696
The imperial doctor said

0:34:48.330,0:34:50.240
that I am one month pregnant.

0:34:51.040,0:34:52.790
My prenatal qi is not stable yet,

0:34:52.790,0:34:55.080
so I shouldn't drink tea for now.

0:35:05.140,0:35:06.890
This careless maid is new to the palace.

0:35:06.890,0:35:09.600
So clumsy she can't even clean a dress rack properly.

0:35:09.890,0:35:11.140
Sorry to disturb Your Highness.

0:35:15.980,0:35:17.209
What's wrong with you?

0:35:17.400,0:35:18.640
Hold the rack up now!

0:35:19.280,0:35:21.529
Stop crying. Her Highness and Her Ladyship are out there.

0:35:21.820,0:35:23.024
Don't disturb them.

0:35:32.710,0:35:34.080
That is wonderful news.

0:35:36.130,0:35:38.921
I failed to discipline the maids well.

0:35:39.220,0:35:40.640
Please forgive me, Your Ladyship.

0:35:40.970,0:35:43.501
New maids are usually careless.

0:35:44.100,0:35:46.570
Our estate is orderly all thanks to Yuyin's abilities.

0:35:46.810,0:35:48.057
If it was me,

0:35:48.390,0:35:50.457
I wouldn't be capable of supervising the servants.

0:35:50.980,0:35:53.967
Yuyin is competent, but that doesn't compare

0:35:53.967,0:35:56.674
to your contribution of bearing His Lordship's heir.

0:35:58.030,0:36:00.320
Since I married into the family,

0:36:00.570,0:36:01.601
I have always heard

0:36:02.110,0:36:04.730
that His Lordship has loved Yuyin for years.

0:36:05.580,0:36:07.040
That was why he married her.

0:36:08.410,0:36:10.370
Yuyin is deeply devoted to His Lordship.

0:36:11.080,0:36:13.740
Just as Your Ladyship is to His Lordship, as well.

0:36:16.130,0:36:19.710
His Lordship has only sympathy towards me.

0:36:21.380,0:36:23.469
And I'm the only one who knows

0:36:23.840,0:36:26.630
how this pregnancy came about.

0:36:27.560,0:36:29.120
Because only with a child

0:36:29.310,0:36:32.520
will His Lordship's heart dwell with mine.

0:36:33.940,0:36:35.776
But recently I discovered

0:36:36.820,0:36:39.589
that Yuyin is also going to great lengths to please His Lordship.

0:36:40.110,0:36:44.400
If His Lordship and Yuyin are as deeply in love as everyone says,

0:36:44.480,0:36:46.720
why does she need to try so hard to please him?

0:36:48.540,0:36:50.201
Since Your Ladyship has married into the family,

0:36:51.080,0:36:55.040
I would like to share my years of experience in the harem.

0:36:56.420,0:36:58.640
"A suspicious heart brings out ghosts in the dark".

0:36:58.880,0:37:01.440
The deeper you think, the more trouble you may cause.

0:37:02.050,0:37:04.290
Those who don't overthink are the wise ones.

0:37:08.260,0:37:09.319
So I hope.

0:37:10.520,0:37:13.880
But I really can't work out what is the truth.

0:37:14.310,0:37:15.307
As I said,

0:37:15.850,0:37:17.871
you are thinking too much due to your pregnancy.

0:37:18.570,0:37:21.492
Now that I share the pillow with His Lordship,

0:37:21.860,0:37:27.608
I can see many things that others cannot.

0:37:28.200,0:37:30.531
As it should be. This is the nature of marriage.

0:37:37.790,0:37:39.096
I should take my leave.

0:37:54.560,0:37:56.077
Meng Jingxian is too smart.

0:37:56.940,0:37:59.581
One day her suspicions will harm His Lordship.

0:38:00.400,0:38:02.030
She loves His Lordship deeply.

0:38:02.030,0:38:03.831
She will put his well-being first.

0:38:05.700,0:38:08.191
But now she is pregnant with His Lordship's child,

0:38:08.620,0:38:11.752
where is there room for me in the estate?

0:38:13.790,0:38:15.320
Meng Jingxian's unborn child

0:38:15.370,0:38:17.160
is His Lordship's rightful heir.

0:38:18.500,0:38:20.240
You are the child's mother in name.

0:38:20.840,0:38:22.482
Of course there is room for you.

0:38:23.300,0:38:25.120
You are the second daughter of our Niohuru family,

0:38:25.300,0:38:27.084
and the lord consort of Noble Prince Guo.

0:38:27.300,0:38:28.803
Your virtue should befit your status.

0:38:33.930,0:38:35.430
I love His Lordship deeply

0:38:36.430,0:38:38.240
and I will naturally treat his child well.

0:38:40.560,0:38:41.798
But Elder Sister,

0:38:43.730,0:38:45.165
my heart is bitter.

0:38:49.490,0:38:51.389
What happened in the past is of no importance.

0:38:52.030,0:38:53.503
The present is what matters.

0:38:54.540,0:38:56.161
His Majesty holds Meng Jingxian in high regard

0:38:57.290,0:38:59.370
and this is the firstborn to the estate.

0:39:00.920,0:39:02.400
You ought to take good care of her,

0:39:02.750,0:39:04.084
and let no harm come to her.

0:39:07.510,0:39:09.304
"I shall be known and loved by you"

0:39:10.510,0:39:12.391
"long without decay or an end."

0:39:12.806,0:39:14.362
["By Heaven" from Shijing]

0:39:15.390,0:39:17.100
"I shall be known and loved by you"

0:39:19.390,0:39:21.060
"long without decay or an end."

0:39:21.860,0:39:23.011
Third Prince,

0:39:23.011,0:39:26.733
I've been hearing you reciting these lines for days now.

0:39:27.820,0:39:28.691
Xiao-Lezi,

0:39:31.450,0:39:32.570
am I unworthy?

0:39:32.570,0:39:33.910
Quite the opposite. Why?

0:39:34.330,0:39:35.849
You are the pride of Heaven.

0:39:36.120,0:39:37.586
What's the point of being Heaven's pride?

0:39:38.750,0:39:40.264
There is only one person

0:39:41.420,0:39:42.560
who cares about me.

0:39:42.960,0:39:44.000
Who?

0:39:46.250,0:39:49.424
Look, words are filling up my heart and lungs

0:39:50.220,0:39:52.069
but I don't know how to tell them to her.

0:39:52.470,0:39:55.294
Master, if you can't speak, why not write?

0:39:58.310,0:39:59.536
Aren't you clever!

0:40:24.790,0:40:27.830
What did your Imperial Mother summon you for?

0:40:28.800,0:40:30.467
Imperial Mother said now that I've come of age,

0:40:31.010,0:40:32.608
Father will arrange a marriage for me.

0:40:33.010,0:40:35.200
The girl surnamed Fuca is a fine lady.

0:40:35.275,0:40:36.684
I have faith in her.

0:40:36.684,0:40:38.080
I trust your judgment, Mother.

0:40:38.310,0:40:40.970
But I am still young, and having a primary wife will be enough.

0:40:41.310,0:40:44.480
Yet Imperial Mother wishes me to also take  
the lady surnamed Ula-Nara as my lord consort.

0:40:45.150,0:40:47.430
Mother, have you heard she is...

0:40:47.430,0:40:48.642
I know it all.

0:40:50.110,0:40:52.607
Since Her Majesty requested, you should agree.

0:40:53.280,0:40:55.256
There's no need to offend her over a trifle.

0:40:55.870,0:40:57.830
But she was rejected by my third brother.

0:40:57.830,0:40:59.354
Assigning her to me...

0:41:01.250,0:41:03.289
The Third Prince rejected her, but you will accommodate her.

0:41:03.540,0:41:05.026
That only shows your generosity.

0:41:05.750,0:41:08.490
Your brother's willful action will now do you a favor.

0:41:09.880,0:41:11.583
She will be merely a lord consort.

0:41:11.840,0:41:14.210
Just marry her and keep her well provided for at home.

0:41:14.970,0:41:17.238
No one is asking you to bow like a maid and serve her.

0:41:17.930,0:41:18.761
Yes.

0:41:19.390,0:41:21.107
If you really dislike Qingying,

0:41:21.560,0:41:23.360
I have one more candidate in mind.

0:41:24.140,0:41:27.187
The lady surnamed Gao who's been taking care of you -
She's gentle and virtuous.

0:41:27.860,0:41:29.440
I also know that you like her.

0:41:30.570,0:41:31.903
Wait a couple years

0:41:32.320,0:41:33.780
and I will request His Majesty

0:41:33.780,0:41:35.617
to decree her to be your Lord Consort.

0:41:35.820,0:41:38.230
Mother, you've been thinking for me.

0:41:38.700,0:41:40.160
I understand the bigger picture

0:41:40.490,0:41:42.120
and won't make things difficult for Mother.

0:41:42.950,0:41:43.910
That's good.

0:41:45.420,0:41:46.626
Peace to Your Highness.

0:41:46.830,0:41:47.700
Please rise.

0:41:48.380,0:41:50.576
His Majesty invites Your Highness
to the Hall of Mental Cultivation.

0:41:51.090,0:41:52.420
I will leave right away.

